@0 = ~Gives kensai abilities to any class~
@1 = ~Kensaisator Ring~
@2 = ~Put this ring on your finger to become a kensai.

PARAMETERS:

Gives the abilities of a kensai to any class:
- Armor Class: +2
- Hit and damage: +1 every 3 levels
- Initiative: +1 and +1 every 4 levels
- Kai ability every 4 levels
- Cannot wear bracelets, armor, or robes (even with the “Use All Items” hla).~